ISLAMABAD, Jan 22 (APP): Prime Minister Shehbaz Sharif Sunday said Imran Niazi had been part of a grand design to oust Nawaz Sharif and victimize Pakistan Muslim League(N) in the name of accountability.
In a tweet on the social media platform Twitter, he said, “From 2013 on, he has been an agent of anarchy and chaos in the country. His poisonous rants have debased politics, polarised society, and undermined state institutions.”
